{"tid":896284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀24歲女應徵文員變陪坐　唔肯「出街」被客人圍毆","createTime":"2018-11-10T01:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T07:53:58.000Z","uid":113626,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d0123c4a8b73130c8145c7aa70f98f0cbe5b642b","tid":896284,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2076140/org/692c77b79c47ee33c7eeca95594084c9.jpg/8Wm-vd8XGkjS9156bM-2bc1Ppb-ZcKZGfbyTUFe8k1A?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2076140%2Forg%2F692c77b79c47ee33c7eeca95594084c9.jpg%2F8Wm-vd8XGkjS9156bM-2bc1Ppb-ZcKZGfbyTUFe8k1A%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=1b152a5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨（9日）深夜11時許，警方接獲一名姓梁（24歲）女子報案，指自己於尖沙咀山林道4號一間夜總會內，因事與三名男顧客發生爭執，並遭對方打傷頭部，三人逞兇後逃去無蹤。救護員趕抵將梁女送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，女事主原本應徵「文員」，昨為首日開工，但被職員遊說落場坐檯做小姐「陪坐」，事發時因不肯「出街」而遭客人毆打。警方調查後將案件列作「襲擊」處理，正追緝三名男子歸案。<br />\n<br />\n對腳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c6e84acb42d14760c7cca4d5e8f90b0cb53fae","tid":896284,"uid":86756,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:30:15.000Z","msg":"行得走得<br />\n應該冇事"},{"pid":"7cda073f0091476f2e474e211d411a236bc4d414","tid":896284,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"02c6e84acb42d14760c7cca4d5e8f90b0cb53fae","tid":896284,"uid":86756,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:30:15.000Z","msg":"行得走得<br />\n應該冇事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da186867f6affbf93b50a65275cf7ceae3a733f3","tid":896284,"uid":67338,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:32:28.000Z","msg":"睇D MK裝束<br />\n唔似唔知情喎"},{"pid":"bcc1a178b2f7d5dd082066f04ba5856ffdc0c0ce","tid":896284,"uid":3302,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T